17:25.085 --> 17:28.337
A guy in Florida
named Gus Boulis.

17:28.422 --> 17:31.090
Bankruptcy's just the
tip of his iceberg.

17:31.175 --> 17:32.759
He needs a buyer fast.

17:33.677 --> 17:35.470
It's a very lucrative casino op.

17:35.554 --> 17:37.847
Anybody who can afford
to get in will get rich.

17:40.893 --> 17:42.810
Anyway, Manny said you'd
have some clients...

17:42.895 --> 17:45.438
who might be interested
under the circumstances.

17:48.108 --> 17:50.109
Yeah. Okay, Art.
I'll look into it.

